{
  "stem": "1918.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 465.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I was the best student in the class always.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And go out into the world and have some great profession.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At one point, I think reciting poetry and acting.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And who knows?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All kinds of things, like being a scientist or anything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were just filled with life and desire.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And always, I guess, had high ideas about life's promises.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Which, of course, were all not so in the end.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we had very high desires.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "How did Hitler's rise to power in '33-- in 1933, did it affect your town at all?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Did it affect Hungary?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You see, the country I come from is a very special country in as much as that all of Hitler's doings did not reach us personally until the very end.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then it reached us with a greater bang, perhaps, than any other country because Hungary was an ally of Hitler.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he didn't have to march into Hungary to get a food-rich country like Hungary to rob the country of all its best food in order to feed his own people so there would be no uprising in Germany, I suppose.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we, we were relatively-- we felt relatively safe, even though anti-Semitism was our daily bread from the day I remember.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I could never walk down the street without being called dirty Jew, dirty Jew, [NON-ENGLISH], a smelly Jew, by the very classmates I had.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Partly, they were envious because I was a good student and because that was the name of the game, hate the Jews.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I do not remember-- I never remember not feeling anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We thought that's the way it is all over the world.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And certainly, that way in Kisvarda.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And you simply have to endure it.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
